{
  "stem": "1363.4",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It is dreams-- and when I have my eyes closed, I could still see what's happened in my dream.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, none.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that is something which I'm very surprised.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Most probably, again, my strength is-- which is the toughness, that it didn't affect me so much like other people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would like [SIGHS] them to stay Jewish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't say that they have to be Bible-bashers, but stay Jewish.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Have the feeling, more to the race as to the religion.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There's a way of life to be Jewish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There is a way of feeling to be Jewish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I don't know whether, has it got anything to do with my upbringing from Grandma, because she put this Jewishness into me, not my mother.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I still, to the very day, use words which I have heard from my grandmother 50 years ago.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And maybe I even teaching my children to-- these lang-- these words.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I feel that it's important to keep-- keep it within yourself, and to transport it into your children, into my grandchildren, et cetera, et cetera, certain habits what we had and certain ways we are living.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Makes us stronger to survive it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Makes it stronger, more determined.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We are a race which we should continue having.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We should be--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, definitely.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wouldn't-- I wouldn't-- I'm happy to be Jewish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Many times, you make a joke at, whether you're happy or not, you're still Jewish, so might as well be happy and proud.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's what I am.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I wouldn't like to be anything else, as I wouldn't like to be anything else as a female.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In spite of having taken over quite a long years, a male role.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] circumstances brought me to it.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
